WEBVTT

00:04.277 --> 00:07.445
SUMNER'S RETURN

00:15.032 --> 00:19.325
- Oh, hi.
- I know you're surprised to see me.

00:20.951 --> 00:25.869
But it's taken every ounce of courage
to show my face here today.

00:26.078 --> 00:29.746
Come on. We get a lot of funny looking
faces in here.

00:32.706 --> 00:35.290
You don't remember me, do you?

00:35.499 --> 00:41.377
I'm Professor Sumner Sloan. I came
in severaI months ago with Diane.

00:41.585 --> 00:45.711
To my shame, I deserted her here
to go back to my ex-wife.

00:45.878 --> 00:51.130
- What can I get for you?
- I'll have a glass of white wine.

00:51.339 --> 00:57.092
Over dinner last night, a mutuaI friend
told me she works here. Is that correct?

00:57.300 --> 01:00.260
I don't know. I wasn't at the dinner.

01:05.512 --> 01:07.513
You slime.

01:08.471 --> 01:13.474
You are a totaI scuzzball.
You're not fit to live with sewer rats.

01:13.683 --> 01:18.601
- I can't defend myself.
- I thought she was talking to me.

